r = requests.post("https://your-space-url.hf.space/run/predict", json={
    "data": ["your input"]
})
print(r.json())
```

Not this:

```python
requests.post("https://your-space-url.hf.space/")
```

---

### ğŸ”¹ **If youâ€™re embedding JS/HTML in the Space**

Use:

```js
